parameters:
Dynamite Abalone: Ugh... so strong... where is this power
coming from...?! Haa haa... but still...

Memimi: Damn it... my attacks are hitting, but the damage
isn't enough... I'm getting tired...

Brachiocondor: This is bad... If it were the usual Shark
Broccoli, he could have powered through with brute force...
but now, he's weakened from repeated humiliation. We need to
break through that abalone armor quickly!
Shark Broccoli: Leave it to me... Shark Broccoli, use this!!

Memimi: Aahh... th-this is the Great Leader's Shark Head!!
With these fangs that have crushed many a monster... abalone
armor is nothing...!

Dynamite Abalone: What are you babbling about! Take this...
Abalone Explosion...

Memimi: We won... such incredible power...!! This is the
strength of the legendary monster, Shark Broccoli the Great
Leader...

??? : Well done, Shark Broccoli!! Though I am no longer a
broccoli or a shark... seeing the splendid growth of my
subordinate, I have no regrets...

??? : She's fainted... It seems the damage had
accumulated...

With the power of the Great Leader, Memimi defeated the once
strongest monster in the city...
